channel.title: || massacred world 317 client || skillcape emotes all 474 gfx items ||
channel.description:
This is the client im using for my current server, its got all skillcape emotes, all 474 gfx and emotes; rocktails as models all pvp armors and all spirit shields.
Download: http://uppit.com/7131udp9w58c/Backup.rar
[b][U]Features:[/U][/b]
-Combat levels work -All gameframe/name options are configured -All emote buttons are configured -Skillcape emotes work -New background -Good Jframe instead of crap windows -Rocktails configured -New maps + objects -All items configured -Skillcapes -Donator tab -Changing gameframe -LOADS MORE!
I think its still configured to server ip, but owell.
[u][b]Pictures:[/b][/u]
New account info and jframe [IMG]http://img259.imageshack.us/img259/6410/newaccoutn.png[/img]
New shop interface [IMG]http://img837.imageshack.us/img837/2244/newshops.png[/img]
New bank configured ("bank all" removed) [IMG]http://img830.imageshack.us/img830/12/configuredbank.png[/img]
New lunar interface configured [IMG]http://img841.imageshack.us/img841/3170/lunarinterfaceworks.png[/img]
Skillcape emotes [IMG]http://img259.imageshack.us/img259/6937/skillcapeemotesandbutto.png[/img]
Options work [IMG]http://img844.imageshack.us/img844/3108/changinggameframeandnam.png[/img]
Clan chat [IMG]http://img841.imageshack.us/img841/243/clanchatworks.png[/img]
My donator tab [IMG]http://img137.imageshack.us/img137/3249/donatoroptions.png[/img]
Combat levels show [IMG]http://img201.imageshack.us/img201/3305/combatleveltextconfigur.png[/img]
[B]100% OPEN SOURCE[/B] POST ANY PROBLEMS OR W/E HERE! THIS TOOK ME ADGES!
[code]Go to client.java, search for "server =" Should come up with server = 64.344.3434. (or whatever) Change that to your IP /localhost Compile[/code]
